> twelve matter particles, plus a group of force-carrying particles to hold them all together

## Elementary Particles

### Leptons

* electron
* muon
* tau
* electron neutrino
* muon neutrino
* tau neutrino

### Quarks

Coloured, interact through gluons.

* up
* down
* charm
* strange
* top
* bottom

### Gauge Bosons

Coloured.

* gluon
* photon
* Z boson
* W boson
* Higgs boson

## Composite Particles

Hadrons (baryons, mesons) are bound states of quarks.

